{"tid":1625553,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"連登全日就係叫人呢三日休息同唔好爆鋪","createTime":"2019-10-05T07:20:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T10:38:11.000Z","uid":132587,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"237793da39adab0dd4f7418758d9d30deeba6363","tid":1625553,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:20:12.000Z","msg":"成個連登風向就係呢三日休息 咩養精畜銳<br />\n又叫人唔好裝修 唔好爆交通燈 <br />\n之後就攞和理非 同驚民意逆轉出黎做擋箭牌<br />\n<br />\n我係政府真係喜聞樂見<br />\n一立法就個個乖乖地留係屋企<br />\n<br />\n到宜家都仲擔心爆鋪會影響民情<br />\n麻雀鋪 360同smartone都出黎澄清都可以話無影響力<br />\n爆鋪已經係我地宜家能力範圍內 對對家最有威脅同可以做既事<br />\n又話攬炒 又驚爆鋪 仲要係中資鋪 即係點?"},{"pid":"67e00681bdd713eaf59efeeebe7653e0219f5358","tid":1625553,"uid":288351,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:23:18.000Z","msg":"擺明有鬼帶風向想爭取時間部署。"},{"pid":"cdbb4705ba0d310beafdc9e3e23506d0a06f005d","tid":1625553,"uid":35604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:25:44.000Z","msg":"好撚多狗係到吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db933c53dfc3259877f1056117e660c7ec644922","tid":1625553,"uid":5258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:29:04.000Z","msg":"今日啲和理非帶哂口罩出哂去<br />\n有一家大細 有銀髮 有輪椅<br />\n得班連登仔叫人休息"},{"pid":"37ad7edc7f9b79d67e51e3dc7f38f48c6f04fa26","tid":1625553,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67e00681bdd713eaf59efeeebe7653e0219f5358","tid":1625553,"uid":288351,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:23:18.000Z","msg":"擺明有鬼帶風向想爭取時間部署。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:01:25.000Z","msg":"今朝起身以為贏左<br />\n叫人休息同唔好爆中資鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f132cc6189574ac22f1f5642f4fc771cc085355d","tid":1625553,"uid":283494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:33:17.000Z","msg":"文宣拆解方向:<br />\n<br />\n咁多爆商舖,係官逼民反呀"},{"pid":"b326814376f